.TH LIST\-PR\-MU2E 1 "April 2026" "DAQ-ControlRoom" "Mu2e DAQ Utilities"
.SH NAME
list\-pr\-mu2e \- list open pull requests across all Mu2e organisation repositories
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B list_pr_mu2e.sh
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B list_pr_mu2e.sh
enumerates every repository in the
.B mu2e
GitHub organisation (up to 4000 repositories) and prints the open pull
requests for each one.
.PP
For each repository discovered by
.BR "gh repo list" ,
it runs
.B gh pr list
and writes the results to standard output.
Repositories with no open pull requests produce no output.
.SH PREREQUISITES
.TP
.BR gh (1)
GitHub CLI, authenticated via
.B gh auth login
or a
.B GITHUB_TOKEN
environment variable.
.SH EXIT STATUS
Exits with the status of the last
.B gh pr list
invocation.
Individual repository failures print an error and continue.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
List all open pull requests across the organisation:
.PP
.nf
bash list_pr_mu2e.sh
.fi
.PP
Filter to repositories with activity:
.PP
.nf
bash list_pr_mu2e.sh | grep -v '^$'
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR gh (1),
.BR list\-issues\-mu2e (1)
